	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories Johannesburg - The body of a man was found under a Brakpan bridge on Sunday morning. Police spokesperson Captain Mavela Masondo said police received information of a body on Snake Road at about 08:00 and on arrival found a man with a gunshot wound to the head. Paramedics were summoned who certified him dead. The motive for the 36-year-old man’s murder was not yet known, Masondo said. “The deceased has been identified and was last seen alive [on Saturday].”   24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  